<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>فخذ من المهدية بالعراق.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>العزاوي ٤/ ٢١٠<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
